Host: 127.0.0.1:%HTTPPORT
Pragma: no-cache
Accept: */*

POST /176 HTTP/1.1
User-Agent: curl/7.12.1-CVS (i686-pc-linux-gnu) libcurl/7.12.1-CVS OpenSSL/0.9.6b ipv6 zlib/1.1.4 GSS libidn/0.4.6
Host: 127.0.0.1:%HTTPPORT
